21:02.462 --> 21:04.063
- SO AUDREY, WE'RE LOOKING
FOR A LITTLE GUIDANCE

21:04.096 --> 21:07.467
ON HOW TO NAIL THIS GUY.

21:07.500 --> 21:09.336
- HE'S POKING HOLES
IN CONDOMS, ISN'T HE?

21:09.369 --> 21:11.404
- MM-HMM, AND UNFORTUNATELY,
THAT'S NOT ILLEGAL.

21:11.438 --> 21:13.573
- PUTTING SEMEN IN A WOMAN
WITHOUT HER CONSENT

21:13.606 --> 21:15.308
SHOULD BE CONSIDERED RAPE.

21:15.342 --> 21:17.344
- THE A.D.A.
DOESN'T SEE IT THAT WAY.

21:17.377 --> 21:19.846
SO, IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
THAT GUYS LIKE THIS DO?

21:19.879 --> 21:22.382
- REPRODUCTIVE ABUSERS
USE VERBAL COERCION

21:22.415 --> 21:24.083
TO MAKE WOMEN HAVE BABIES.

21:24.116 --> 21:26.419
- WE CAN'T COLLAR THIS GUY
FOR WHAT COMES OUT OF HIS MOUTH.

21:26.453 --> 21:28.054
- WHEN THEIR WORDS DON'T WORK,

21:28.087 --> 21:30.323
SOME USE THEIR FISTS
TO GET WHAT THEY WANT.

21:30.357 --> 21:32.692
- THERE'S NO EVIDENCE
KEN IS HITTING DEDE.

21:32.725 --> 21:35.094
- BUT WE DO HAVE KEN'S
20 OTHER BABY-MAMAS TO ASK.

21:35.127 --> 21:36.195
WE SHOULD TRACK THEM DOWN.

21:36.228 --> 21:38.598
- SEE IF KEN IS BEATING
ANY OF THEM INTO SUBMISSION.

21:38.631 --> 21:40.367
- OR WENT
EVEN FURTHER THAN FISTS.

21:40.400 --> 21:42.535
SOMETIMES VERBAL
COERCION LEADS TO RAPE.

21:42.569 --> 21:44.837
REAL, PROSECUTABLE RAPE.

21:44.871 --> 21:46.439
- WE'RE BOUND
TO FIND SOMETHING

21:46.473 --> 21:47.707
IF WE KICK OVER
ENOUGH ROCKS.

21:47.740 --> 21:50.510
- I KNOW ONE
WE CAN START KICKING.

21:50.543 --> 21:54.113
I FOUND JASPER'S
BIRTH CERTIFICATE.

21:54.146 --> 21:55.615
HADN'T BEEN FILED.

21:55.648 --> 21:58.351
WHAT I DIDN'T FIND WAS ANY
RECORD OF ADOPTION.

21:58.385 --> 21:59.519
- DEDE THINKS IT'S LEGAL.

21:59.552 --> 22:02.755
- WELL, LET'S ASK JASPER'S
BIRTH-MOTHER IF SHE AGREES.

22:04.991 --> 22:06.459
- KEN RENTED SKATES
FROM ME,

22:06.493 --> 22:08.561
CHATTED ME UP,
ASKED ME OUT ON A DATE.

22:08.595 --> 22:10.963
WE ONLY HAD SEX ONCE.

22:10.997 --> 22:15.402
BUT THEN HE FOUND OUT
I GOT...PROBLEMS.

22:15.435 --> 22:16.736
- WHAT ARE YOU USING,
BRIDGET?

22:16.769 --> 22:18.771
- WHATEVER YOU GOT.

22:20.773 --> 22:23.443
- SO LET ME GUESS,
YOU GOT PREGNANT.

22:23.476 --> 22:24.744
YOU THOUGHT THAT
KEN WOULD DISAPPEAR

22:24.777 --> 22:28.080
BECAUSE YOU'RE AN ADDICT.
BUT HE WAS THRILLED.

22:28.114 --> 22:30.950
- I ONLY WANTED HIM
TO PAY FOR THE ABORTION,

22:30.983 --> 22:34.020
BUT BEFORE I KNEW IT, KEN...
[chuckles]

22:34.053 --> 22:35.688
CHECKED ME INTO REHAB,

22:35.722 --> 22:38.124
RENTED ME
A NICE APARTMENT,

22:38.157 --> 22:41.428
EVEN PROMISED TO
MARRY ME.

22:41.461 --> 22:42.729
- A WHOLE NEW LIFE
FROM ONE CONDOM

22:42.762 --> 22:44.163
THAT ACCIDENTALLY RIPPED.

22:44.196 --> 22:47.066
- AT FIRST,
IT WAS AMAZING.

22:47.099 --> 22:50.837
I WAS CLEAN...
IN LOVE.

22:50.870 --> 22:54.006
MY BEAUTIFUL BOY
GROWING INSIDE ME...

22:54.040 --> 22:55.174
- SO WHY'D
YOU GIVE HIM UP?

22:55.207 --> 22:57.109
- THE WEEK JASPER
WAS BORN,

22:57.143 --> 23:00.146
SOME FRIENDS OF MY FRIENDS
CAME TO SEE HIM.

23:01.614 --> 23:03.883
I JUST DID
A LITTLE BLOW, BUT...

23:03.916 --> 23:05.184
- KEN FOUND OUT.

23:05.217 --> 23:06.819
SAID YOU WEREN'T FIT
FOR MOTHERHOOD.

23:06.853 --> 23:10.457
- HE WASN'T MEAN
ABOUT IT.

23:10.490 --> 23:13.626
HE SAID HE FOUND
SOMEONE WHO WOULD

23:13.660 --> 23:15.495
GIVE JASPER A BETTER LIFE.

23:15.528 --> 23:17.196
SAID IF I REALLY CARED,

23:17.229 --> 23:19.065
THEN I'D SEE
I HAD NO CHOICE.

23:19.098 --> 23:21.468
- BUT YOU
DID HAVE A CHOICE.

23:21.501 --> 23:23.970
- IT'S SO HARD TO THINK
WHEN KEN WAS AROUND.

23:24.003 --> 23:27.774
THE WAY HE TALKS,
HE'S...SO CONVINCING.

23:29.509 --> 23:33.680
HE TOOK
MY LITTLE JASPER.

23:33.713 --> 23:36.783
I CAN STILL SEE
KEN CARRYING HIM AWAY.

23:39.486 --> 23:42.489
HIS LITTLE CHEEKS.

23:46.258 --> 23:48.828
- BRIDGET, DID YOU EVER
TRY TO GET JASPER BACK?

23:48.861 --> 23:51.130
- YEAH.

23:51.163 --> 23:53.666
YEAH, TWO WEEKS AFTER.

23:53.700 --> 23:56.002
BUT KEN SAID
IT WAS TOO LATE.

23:56.035 --> 23:59.238
- A BIRTHMOTHER HAS 45 DAYS
TO CHANGE HER MIND.

23:59.271 --> 24:01.974
- YEAH, THAT'S WHAT THEY TOLD ME
WHEN I WENT DOWN TO CITY HALL.

24:02.008 --> 24:05.111
BUT THERE WAS
NO ADOPTION RECORD,

24:05.144 --> 24:06.646
SO THERE WAS
NOTHING I COULD DO.

24:06.679 --> 24:07.780
- DID YOU SIGN PAPERWORK?

24:07.814 --> 24:10.717
- YEAH.
HE CONVINCED ME TO.

24:12.284 --> 24:15.087
- BRIDGET, DO YOU
STILL WANT YOUR SON BACK?

24:15.121 --> 24:19.058
- MORE THAN ANYTHING
IN THE WORLD.

24:25.231 --> 24:27.700
- FINALLY SOMETHING
WE CAN ARREST HIM FOR.

24:27.734 --> 24:29.602
- I HOPE SO.
- HOPE SO?

24:29.636 --> 24:30.903
KEN DIDN'T FILE
THE PAPERWORK.

24:30.937 --> 24:32.271
THAT MEANS
HE STOLE BRIDGET'S BABY.

24:32.304 --> 24:35.675
- AND THOSE WARRANTS CAN BE
PRETTY TRICKY TO GET.

24:35.708 --> 24:37.243
- YEAH, OUR SYSTEM'S READY,

24:37.276 --> 24:39.278
SO JUST SEND IT.
OKAY, THANKS.

24:39.311 --> 24:40.146
- DID IT GO THROUGH?

24:40.179 --> 24:42.982
- THE WARRANT
TO LOCATE KENNETH TURNER

24:43.015 --> 24:46.018
VIA CELL PHONE GPS
HAS BEEN EXECUTED.

24:46.052 --> 24:47.153
AND THERE YOU GO.

24:47.186 --> 24:49.021
- OKAY, 65TH AND LEXINGTON.

24:49.055 --> 24:50.256
THERE'S
A FLOWER SHOP THERE.

24:50.289 --> 24:52.158
- HOW MUCH YOU WANNA BET
HE'S NOT BUYING ROSES

24:52.191 --> 24:54.126
FOR HIS SICK GRANNY?

24:54.160 --> 24:56.162
- HE'S ON THE MOVE,
WALKING ACROSS THE STREET.

24:56.195 --> 24:58.230
- YOU GUYS KNOW
WHAT'S THERE, RIGHT?

24:58.264 --> 25:01.300
- THAT NEW HOTEL.
THE AHIMSA.

25:01.333 --> 25:04.303
- VERY HIGH-END.
VERY ROMANTIC.

25:04.336 --> 25:07.540
- THAT SON-OF-A-BITCH
HAS ANOTHER DATE.

25:19.285 --> 25:21.053
- GET READY, STACY,
BECAUSE I'M GONNA

25:21.087 --> 25:22.121
ROCK YOUR WORLD...

25:22.154 --> 25:24.591
- ESPECIALLY WHEN
SHE FINDS OUT SHE'S PREGNANT.

25:24.624 --> 25:25.692
- WHAT THE HELL?

25:25.725 --> 25:28.027
- GET DRESSED.
PARTY'S OVER.

25:28.060 --> 25:29.261
- ON WHAT THE CHARGE?

25:29.295 --> 25:33.032
- ENDANGERING THE WELFARE OF
A CHILD AND AN ILLEGAL ADOPTION.

25:33.065 --> 25:34.834
YOU FAILED TO
FILE THE PAPERWORK.

25:34.867 --> 25:36.736
- WHY SHOULD I?
I'M JASPER'S FATHER.

25:36.769 --> 25:39.772
- YOU GAVE HIM OVER TO DEDE
WITHOUT THE MOTHER'S CONSENT.

25:39.806 --> 25:44.677
DON'T THINK THE JURY IS GONNA
LOOK TOO KINDLY UPON THAT.

25:44.711 --> 25:46.613
- KEN,
THIS IS A MISTAKE, RIGHT?

25:46.646 --> 25:48.314
- ANOTHER
BOUNCING BABY MISTAKE

25:48.347 --> 25:49.682
IF HE USED THIS ON YOU.

25:49.716 --> 25:52.652
HOLD IT UP TO THE LIGHT.

25:54.621 --> 25:56.288
- SEE, YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.
I'M A GOOD GUY.

25:56.322 --> 25:58.958
- WHO RIPS HIS NEWBORN BABY AWAY
FROM HIS BIOLOGICAL MOTHER.

25:58.991 --> 26:00.693
- BRIDGET'S A COKE FIEND!

26:00.727 --> 26:02.595
SHE'S NOT FIT
TO RAISE MY CHILD.

26:02.629 --> 26:04.230
- YEAH, BUT IT ALSO HAPPENS
TO BE HER CHILD,

26:04.263 --> 26:07.233
AND SHE HAS A RIGHT TO
DECIDE HIS FATE.

26:07.266 --> 26:08.635
SEE, YOU TRIED
TO DO A LITTLE END-AROUND

26:08.668 --> 26:09.936
BY NOT FILING THAT PAPERWORK.

26:09.969 --> 26:10.937
- A MISDEMEANOR.

26:10.970 --> 26:13.239
SEEMS A LITTLE BENEATH

26:13.272 --> 26:14.907
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT,
DOESN'T IT?

26:14.941 --> 26:17.644
- WELL...
WE TAKE ALL CRIME SERIOUSLY.

26:17.677 --> 26:20.079
- SINCE WHEN IS IT A CRIME
TO GIVE JASPER A BETTER MOTHER?

26:20.112 --> 26:22.782
DEDE'S STABLE,
SHE'S SECURE...

26:22.815 --> 26:24.083
- AND YOU LIKE HER SO MUCH

26:24.116 --> 26:26.185
THAT YOU USED
THE OLD BROKEN CONDOM ROUTINE

26:26.218 --> 26:28.087
TO MAKE SURE
THAT YOU KNOCKED HER UP.

26:28.120 --> 26:29.288
- WHY DO YOU HAVE
SUCH A HARD-ON FOR ME?

26:29.321 --> 26:32.925
- 'CAUSE YOU CAN'T KEEP YOURS
OUT OF UNSUSPECTING WOMEN.

26:32.959 --> 26:33.726
- I'M JUST TRYING TO FOLLOW

26:33.760 --> 26:36.062
MY NATURAL
MALE URGE TO PROCREATE.

26:36.095 --> 26:38.698
- NO, YOU TURN PEOPLE'S
LIVES UPSIDE-DOWN.

26:38.731 --> 26:41.668
- NO, I'M MAKING
THEIR LIVES RICHER.

26:41.701 --> 26:44.704
WITH MY PROGENY,
AND MY MONEY.

26:46.138 --> 26:49.208
WHAT ABOUT YOU, DETECTIVE?
YOU GOT KIDS?

26:49.241 --> 26:50.376
- YEAH, WITH MY WIFE.

26:50.409 --> 26:53.646
- HOW MANY?

26:53.680 --> 26:54.747
- NOT AS MANY AS YOU.

26:54.781 --> 26:56.215
- HOW MANY, DETECTIVE?

27:01.721 --> 27:04.323
- FIVE.
- FIVE CHILDREN?

27:04.356 --> 27:05.792
THAT'S INTERESTING.

27:05.825 --> 27:09.361
YOU KNOW, THE NATIONAL
AVERAGE IS 1.83.

27:09.395 --> 27:13.332
SEE, I THINK
YOU UNDERSTAND THE URGE,

27:13.365 --> 27:16.936
BUT YOU'RE LIMITED
BY FEAR OR WEAKNESS OR...

27:16.969 --> 27:20.339
LACK OF MEANS...
LACK OF MOJO.

27:20.372 --> 27:23.175
- [chuckles]
- SEE, AT HEART...

27:23.209 --> 27:26.012
I THINK YOU
YOU REALLY WANT TO BE ME.

27:26.045 --> 27:28.314
- A SAD, LITTLE MAN WITH
AN INFERIORITY COMPLEX

27:28.347 --> 27:30.750
TRYING SO DESPERATELY
TO MAKE UP FOR IT.

27:30.783 --> 27:34.320
- INFERIORITY COMPLEX?
NO, I'M MONTEZUMA, MAN.

27:34.353 --> 27:35.254
- [chuckles]

27:35.287 --> 27:38.224
- THE AZTEC LEADER
WITH 4,000 CONCUBINES

27:38.257 --> 27:39.959
AND WHO KNOWS
HOW MANY KIDS--

27:39.992 --> 27:41.393
- AND WHO PRACTICED
HUMAN SACRIFICE.

27:41.427 --> 27:43.295
- [chuckles]
- YOU KNOW HOW I KNOW THAT?

27:43.329 --> 27:45.898
- MM, BECAUSE
YOU PASSED SEVENTH GRADE.

27:45.932 --> 27:47.166
- I HELPED MY CHILDREN

27:47.199 --> 27:48.935
WITH THEIR HOMEWORK
EVERY NIGHT.

27:50.336 --> 27:51.938
AND I GAVE THEM LOVE

27:51.971 --> 27:56.275
AND I GAVE THEM ATTENTION
EVERY DAY.

27:56.308 --> 27:58.210
NOW, HOW MUCH TIME
DO YOU SPEND WITH YOUR KIDS?

27:58.244 --> 28:00.980
'CAUSE IT SEEMS
TO ME YOU SPEND ALL OF IT

28:01.013 --> 28:03.149
TRYING TO MAKING MORE.

28:03.182 --> 28:07.053
SEE, BEING A FATHER
IS ABOUT SUPPORT,

28:07.086 --> 28:09.321
HM?
NOT SPAWN.

28:09.355 --> 28:13.059
- EVERY MAN DREAMS
OF BEDDING LOTS OF WOMEN.

28:13.092 --> 28:15.261
C'MON, ADMIT IT,
DETECTIVE.

28:15.294 --> 28:18.197
YOU KNOW YOU
WANT TO BANG YOUR PARTNER.

28:18.230 --> 28:20.499
WATCH HER GROW SWOLLEN
WITH YOUR CHILD.

28:20.532 --> 28:21.834
AND WHY NOT, MAN?

28:21.868 --> 28:24.236
SHE'D GIVE YOU
BEAUTIFUL BABIES...

28:24.270 --> 28:27.840
- YOU ARE
A SICK SON-OF-A-BITCH.

28:27.874 --> 28:30.877
- [chuckles]

28:32.278 --> 28:35.347
[door opening,
closing loudly]

28:35.381 --> 28:37.249
- HE'S THE WORST
I'VE EVER SEEN.

28:37.283 --> 28:38.284
- THAT'S SAYING A LOT.

28:38.317 --> 28:39.485
HOW LONG
YOU BEEN DOING THIS?

28:39.518 --> 28:41.954
- MY WHOLE LIFE, REALLY.
MOM'S A THERAPIST.

28:41.988 --> 28:43.756
- OH, DAD WAS A COP.

28:43.790 --> 28:46.025
NOT THAT I EVER WANTED
TO FOLLOW IN HIS FOOTSTEPS.

28:46.058 --> 28:47.226
- ME EITHER, BUT...

28:47.259 --> 28:49.962
MY SISTER'S BOYFRIEND BEAT
THE HELL OUT OF HER ONE NIGHT.

28:49.996 --> 28:50.963
NEXT THING I KNOW,

28:50.997 --> 28:54.366
I WAS A DOMESTIC
VIOLENCE COUNSELOR IN BUFFALO.

28:54.400 --> 28:56.268
- WELL,
I HATE TO SAY IT, BUT...

28:56.302 --> 28:58.237
IT MIGHT BE EASIER
IF THIS GUY WAS HITTING WOMEN.

28:58.270 --> 29:02.208
- HIS CHARM IS
WHAT MAKES HIM SO DANGEROUS.

29:02.241 --> 29:04.043
THERE'S NO LIMIT
TO THE NUMBER OF WOMEN

29:04.076 --> 29:05.544
WHOSE LIVES HE CAN WRECK.

29:05.577 --> 29:07.413
THANK GOD
YOU ARRESTED HIM.

29:07.446 --> 29:10.182
- THAT IS NOT GONNA STICK.
- YOU SPOKE WITH HARDWICKE.

29:10.216 --> 29:12.151
- SHE SAID A MISDEMEANOR
IS NOT WORTH HER TIME,

29:12.184 --> 29:15.121
ESPECIALLY SINCE IT RESTS
ON A PAPERWORK TECHNICALITY.

29:15.154 --> 29:16.122
SHE SAID ANY
GOOD DEFENSE ATTORNEY

29:16.155 --> 29:18.190
WOULD GET KEN OFF
WITH A SLAP ON THE WRIST.

29:18.224 --> 29:19.959
- YOU BROUGHT HIM IN
JUST TO LET HIM GO?

29:19.992 --> 29:21.794
- WELL, WE THOUGHT
OUR D.A. MIGHT PUNT,

29:21.828 --> 29:23.295
SO WE HAVE A BACK-UP PLAN.
YOU ALL SET?

29:23.329 --> 29:25.297
- MM-HMM.

29:25.331 --> 29:26.532
- THERE ARE NO CELL PHONES
ALLOWED IN HERE.

29:26.565 --> 29:28.200
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

29:28.234 --> 29:30.502
- YOU KNOW, DETECTIVE,
I'D CONSIDER SUING YOU

29:30.536 --> 29:33.172
FOR HARASSMENT,
BUT FOR YOUR KIDS' SAKE,

29:33.205 --> 29:35.007
I'D HATE TO SEE YOU
LOSE YOUR JOB.

29:35.041 --> 29:38.044
- SWEET OF YOU.
LET ME WALK YOU OUT.

29:47.153 --> 29:49.288
- LOOK, LESLIE,
THERE'S YOUR FATHER!

29:49.321 --> 29:51.891
- [scoffs]
YOUR GIRL'S FATHER?

29:51.924 --> 29:53.459
KEN'S MY BOY'S DAD.

29:53.492 --> 29:55.194
- CUTE, DETECTIVE.
REAL CUTE.

29:55.227 --> 29:58.430
SO NOW I GUESS YOU
EXPECT ME TO WILT, RIGHT?

29:58.464 --> 30:00.266
- KEN, WHAT'S GOING ON?

30:00.299 --> 30:03.903
- WELL, THIS IS THE NYPD'S
VAIN ATTEMPT AT EMBARRASSING ME.

30:03.936 --> 30:06.472
TO MAKE YOU ALL REALIZE
HOW MANY OF YOU THERE ARE.

30:06.505 --> 30:09.141
- YOU SON OF A BITCH!

30:09.175 --> 30:11.443
YOU SAID
I WAS YOUR ONE AND ONLY.

30:11.477 --> 30:13.345
- CLOWN SAID HE'D MARRY ME.

30:13.379 --> 30:15.547
- AND ME.
- [sighs]

30:15.581 --> 30:18.150
- JENNY,
YOU SAID LITTLE LESLIE'S

30:18.184 --> 30:19.518
THE BEST THING
THAT EVER HAPPENED TO YOU.

30:19.551 --> 30:22.288
- AND YOU SAID
WE WERE GOING TO BE A FAMILY.

30:22.321 --> 30:26.292
NOW I'M A SINGLE MOM,
I HAD TO DROP OUT OF MED SCHOOL.

30:26.325 --> 30:29.896
- WELL, MY CHILD'S MORE
IMPORTANT THAN MED SCHOOL.

30:29.929 --> 30:32.631
- AND, KATE, KATE, YOU CALL ME
AT LEAST ONCE A WEEK.

30:32.664 --> 30:36.302
- BECAUSE I WANT YOU
TO SPEND TIME WITH ZACK.

30:36.335 --> 30:38.204
HE'S GROWING UP
WITHOUT A FATHER.

30:38.237 --> 30:40.072
- WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?
I'M A GREAT FATHER.

30:40.106 --> 30:41.407
WHO SENDS A CHECK
EVERY MONTH.

30:41.440 --> 30:44.076
YOU KNOW
I'M YOUR DADDY, HUH?

30:44.110 --> 30:46.378
ATTA BOY.
ALL RIGHT, SON.

30:46.412 --> 30:49.248
DEDE...

30:56.588 --> 30:58.424
I'M SORRY, I DIDN'T
SLEEP WITH YOU, RIGHT?

30:58.457 --> 31:00.326
- [laughing]
NO.

31:00.359 --> 31:02.094
NO, JUST
MY DAUGHTER TRISH.

31:02.128 --> 31:04.463
- OH, TRISH, RIGHT.
HOW'S LITTLE MARK?

31:04.496 --> 31:06.098
THE NAME IS MAX.

31:06.132 --> 31:08.067
AND HE'S DEAD,
JUST LIKE HIS MOTHER.

31:08.100 --> 31:10.269
- WHAT? HOW?

31:10.302 --> 31:13.505
- WHEN YOU REFUSED TO
LET THEM MOVE IN WITH YOU,

31:13.539 --> 31:18.010
TRISH DROVE HOME,
CLOSED THE GARAGE,

31:18.044 --> 31:21.247
AND LEFT
THE MOTOR RUNNING.

31:21.280 --> 31:23.149
SHE THEN
GOT IN THE BACK SEAT

31:23.182 --> 31:25.918
AND READ MAX
GOOD NIGHT, MOON.

31:27.219 --> 31:30.222
UNTIL THEY BOTH DIED
FROM THE CARBON MONOXIDE.

31:34.160 --> 31:36.062
- SHE HAD
NO RIGHT TO KILL MY SON.

31:36.095 --> 31:37.930
- OH, YOU--
- YOU REALLY FEEL YOU HAVE

31:37.964 --> 31:40.199
NO RESPONSIBILITY
IN ANY OF THIS?

31:40.232 --> 31:43.535
- THEY'RE MY CHILDREN.
OF COURSE I FEEL RESPONSIBLE.

31:43.569 --> 31:45.271
I LOVE THAT THEY'RE MINE.

31:45.304 --> 31:46.205
- SHAME ON YOU.

31:46.238 --> 31:49.208
YOU'VE OVERTURNED
THE LIVES OF 20 WOMEN.

31:49.241 --> 31:51.043
- OVERTURNED?
NO.

31:51.077 --> 31:53.312
IMPROVED?
YES.

31:53.345 --> 31:56.515
AND 20?
NOT EVEN CLOSE.

31:56.548 --> 31:58.050
- WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

31:58.084 --> 32:00.219
- YOU ONLY CHECKED
IN NEW YORK.

32:00.252 --> 32:02.955
LOOK AROUND THE COUNTRY,
A BIT INTO EUROPE,

32:02.989 --> 32:05.992
YOU'LL FIND
I HAVE 47 CHILDREN.

32:07.293 --> 32:09.128
AND I LOVE EACH
AND EVERY ONE OF THEM.

32:15.501 --> 32:18.604
[quietly]
MAGGIE!

32:18.637 --> 32:21.607
- IT'S AMAZING THAT A GUY
CAN BLAZE A TRAIL OF DESTRUCTION

32:21.640 --> 32:23.575
SO WIDE AND STILL
NOT DO ANYTHING ILLEGAL.

32:23.609 --> 32:26.045
- WELL, IT TOOK
THE COURTS A LONG TIME

32:26.078 --> 32:28.114
TO RECOGNIZE
DOMESTIC VIOLENCE AS A CRIME.

32:28.147 --> 32:30.249
- MAYBE AUDREY'S RESEARCH
CAN RAISE AWARENESS

32:30.282 --> 32:34.453
ABOUT REPRODUCTIVE COERCION
AND PASS LAWS ABOUT IT.

32:34.486 --> 32:36.755
POKING HOLES IN CONDOMS
WILL BECOME FRAUD

32:36.788 --> 32:37.990
WITH INTENT TO DECEIVE.
- SURE.

32:38.024 --> 32:41.260
FLUSHING BIRTH-CONTROL PILLS
DOWN THE TOILET BECOMES LARCENY.

32:41.293 --> 32:44.163
- AND BEING A WORLD-CLASS CREEP
CAN GET YOU DEAD AS A DOORNAIL.

32:44.196 --> 32:45.497
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

32:45.531 --> 32:47.099
- KEN TURNER
WAS JUST FOUND DEAD

32:47.133 --> 32:49.335
IN THE GARDEN
BEHIND DEDE'S BROWNSTONE.

32:49.368 --> 32:51.303
APPARENTLY,
IT WAS GRUESOME...

32:51.337 --> 32:55.241
JUST WHEN YOU THINK
YOU'VE SEEN EVERYTHING.

32:57.176 --> 32:58.477
- LOOKS LIKE HE ATE A BOMB.

32:58.510 --> 33:00.279
- NEIGHBOR SAID
SHE HEARD A SCREAM

33:00.312 --> 33:02.514
AND THEN WHAT SHE
DESCRIBED AS A "WET BANG."

33:02.548 --> 33:05.351
LOOKS LIKE DEDE WENT
FROM THINKING HE'S MR. PERFECT

33:05.384 --> 33:07.319
TO HATING HIS GUTS.

33:07.353 --> 33:10.389
- ENOUGH TO BLOW 'EM
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

33:21.300 --> 33:22.501
- FIND THE MURDER WEAPON?

33:22.534 --> 33:24.270
- NOT EVEN CLOSE.

33:24.303 --> 33:26.372
NOT THAT I KNOW
WHAT DOES THAT TO A GUY.

33:26.405 --> 33:28.807
- WHATEVER IT IS, DID IT FAST.
NO DEFENSIVE WOUNDS.

33:28.840 --> 33:30.676
- I'M NOT SURE IT WAS DEDE.

33:30.709 --> 33:33.745
HER LIGHTS ARE OUT,
HER MAIL'S ON THE STOOP,

33:33.779 --> 33:36.548
LIKE SHE HASN'T BEEN HOME
SINCE SHE LEFT THE PRECINCT.

33:36.582 --> 33:40.419
- WE'VE GOT ACCESS BACK HERE
FROM WADE FISK'S APARTMENT.

33:40.452 --> 33:42.521
- WADE'S IN CUSTODY
FOR STEALING JASPER.

33:42.554 --> 33:45.557
- UNLESS HE MADE BAIL.

33:48.260 --> 33:49.761
DECIDED TO SLAY
THE MONSTER, HUH?

33:49.795 --> 33:51.730
- I DIDN'T TOUCH KEN,
I SWEAR.

33:51.763 --> 33:53.665
- JUST LIKE YOU SWORE
YOU DIDN'T STEAL JASPER.

33:53.699 --> 33:54.833
- I'M TELLING THE TRUTH.

33:54.866 --> 33:56.335
I MADE BAIL, CAME HOME,

33:56.368 --> 33:57.536
HEARD SOMETHING LOUD
IN BACK.

33:57.569 --> 33:58.704
WENT OUT
TO SEE WHAT IT WAS,

33:58.737 --> 34:01.307
AND THERE WAS KEN...
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

34:01.340 --> 34:03.209
- AND SO YOU FIGURED
IT'S TIME TO SEE EUROPE

34:03.242 --> 34:05.344
LIKE YOU ALWAYS
DREAMED OF.

34:05.377 --> 34:07.413
- IT'S NO SECRET
I HATED THE GUY.

34:07.446 --> 34:09.315
I KNEW YOU'D BLAME ME.

34:09.348 --> 34:11.283
SEARCH MY PLACE.
YOU WON'T FIND ANYTHING.

34:11.317 --> 34:13.352
- OH.

34:13.385 --> 34:16.388
THANKS
FOR THE PERMISSION.

34:27.233 --> 34:29.335
I KNOW HOW YOU KILLED HIM.

34:29.368 --> 34:31.703
IT'S CALLED
A WASP INJECTION KNIFE.

34:31.737 --> 34:33.772
- LOOKS LIKE
A STANDARD DIVE KNIFE.

34:33.805 --> 34:35.674
- BUT IT'S NOT; IT WAS
DEVELOPED FOR THE NAVY SEALS

34:35.707 --> 34:37.809
BECAUSE OF THE SPECIAL PUNCH
THAT IT PACKS.

34:37.843 --> 34:40.279
INSIDE THE HANDLE
IS A CANISTER THAT SHOOTS

34:40.312 --> 34:42.448
A BALL OF COMPRESSED CO2

34:42.481 --> 34:44.750
INTO WHATEVER IT IS
THAT YOU'RE STABBING,

34:44.783 --> 34:48.587
INSTANTLY INFLATING IT
TO THE SIZE OF A BASKETBALL.

34:48.620 --> 34:50.756
- MAKES SENSE FOR DIVING.
YOU STAB A SHARK WITH IT,

34:50.789 --> 34:52.591
AND IT ROCKETS
UP TO THE SURFACE.

34:52.624 --> 34:54.893
- AND IT'S BLOWN
TO BITS BY 800 P.S.I.

34:54.926 --> 34:56.595
- WHOA.

34:56.628 --> 34:58.830
- JUST LIKE KEN.

35:00.232 --> 35:01.833
- WHAT IS THAT?

35:01.867 --> 35:03.335
- THE MURDER WEAPON
YOU USED ON KEN.

35:03.369 --> 35:05.471
- A WASP KNIFE?

35:05.504 --> 35:06.705
- LOOKIE THERE,
HE KNOWS WHAT IT IS.

35:06.738 --> 35:07.506
- JUST BECAUSE
I'M A DIVER DOESN'T MEAN--

35:07.539 --> 35:10.342
- YOU HAD MOTIVE.
YOU HATED KEN.

35:10.376 --> 35:11.877
- AND YOU HAD OPPORTUNITY.

35:11.910 --> 35:13.679
PRIVATE ACCESS
TO THAT BACK GARDEN?

35:13.712 --> 35:16.482
- NO.
DEDE HAS ACCESS...

35:16.515 --> 35:17.716
- OH, SO SHE
WENT DOWN INTO YOUR PLACE

35:17.749 --> 35:18.750
AND STOLE
YOUR KNIFE, HUH?

35:18.784 --> 35:20.652
- DEDE'S A DIVER TOO.

35:20.686 --> 35:21.820
THAT'S HOW
I CAME TO RENT FROM HER.

35:21.853 --> 35:23.855
WE MET ON A DIVE TRIP.

35:23.889 --> 35:27.926
AND DEDE...
OWNS ONE OF THOSE.

35:27.959 --> 35:30.596
- HELL, YES,
I HAVE A WASP KNIFE.

35:30.629 --> 35:32.864
SAVED ME FROM
A HAMMERHEAD IN FLORIDA

35:32.898 --> 35:35.234
ABOUT, UH, TWO YEARS AGO.

35:35.267 --> 35:36.868
- SO WHEN
A SHARK LIKE KEN TURNER

35:36.902 --> 35:38.704
WALKS INTO YOUR LIFE
AND TAKES A BITE OUT OF IT,

35:38.737 --> 35:41.307
YOU FIGURE,
"HEY, IT WORKED ONCE,

35:41.340 --> 35:43.742
IT'LL WORK AGAIN."
- I HATE KEN.

35:43.775 --> 35:46.745
YOU AND DETECTIVE STABLER
CONVINCED ME.

35:46.778 --> 35:49.781
OKAY, I HATE HIM.
[sighs]

35:49.815 --> 35:52.418
BUT HE'S STILL
THE FATHER OF MY BABY.

35:52.451 --> 35:53.885
AND FOR THAT REASON ALONE,
I WOULD NEVER--

35:53.919 --> 35:56.522
- DEDE, THE MAN WAS
KILLED IN YOUR GARDEN

35:56.555 --> 35:59.625
WITH YOUR DIVE KNIFE.

36:01.727 --> 36:04.796
- WELL, SOMEBODY TOOK MY KNIFE
AND USED IT ON HIM.

36:04.830 --> 36:06.798
- SO SOMEBODY ENTERED
YOUR APARTMENT WITH KEN,

36:06.832 --> 36:09.435
FOUND YOUR KNIFE,
USED IT?

36:09.468 --> 36:10.536
OKAY, WHO HAS THE KEY?

36:10.569 --> 36:12.704
- KEN!
HE HAS A KEY.

36:12.738 --> 36:15.807
HE USED MY HOUSE
LIKE HIS DAMN LOVE SHACK.

36:15.841 --> 36:18.210
IT WASN'T JUST IMELDA.

36:18.244 --> 36:20.279
IT WAS DOZENS OF
OTHER WOMEN.

36:20.312 --> 36:23.382
ANYTIME I WAS AWAY.
- AND YOU KNEW ABOUT THIS?

36:23.415 --> 36:25.917
- I'D SMELL PERFUME
OR I SAW THE BED RE-MADE.

36:25.951 --> 36:31.223
BUT I WOULDN'T LET MYSELF
BELIEVE IT, I GUESS, I--

36:31.257 --> 36:34.560
YOU KNOW, KEN WAS SO GOOD
AT SWEET-TALKING YOU,

36:34.593 --> 36:37.729
AND SAID HE HAD NO INTEREST
IN YOUNGER WOMEN.

36:37.763 --> 36:39.265
- REMINDING YOU
OF YOUR AGE.

36:39.298 --> 36:40.599
EXPLOITING YOUR FEAR
OF LOSING HIM...

36:40.632 --> 36:42.401
- LAST NIGHT,
THAT'S WHAT THEY ALL SAID.

36:42.434 --> 36:46.738
KEN COULD SWEET-TALK YOU OUT OF
ANY SUSPICION YOU MIGHT HAVE.

36:46.772 --> 36:50.676
- ALL WHO?
- THE WOMEN YOU BROUGHT IN.

36:50.709 --> 36:53.512
LAST NIGHT,
AFTER KEN LEFT, UM...

36:53.545 --> 36:56.848
AUDREY SUGGESTED THAT WE GO
TO A RESTAURANT

36:56.882 --> 37:00.519
DOWN THE STREET AND TALK
ABOUT WHAT KEN HAD DONE TO US.

37:00.552 --> 37:03.822
AND THAT'S WHERE I WAS
WHEN, UM...

37:03.855 --> 37:05.724
WHEN KEN WAS MURDERED.

37:05.757 --> 37:06.825
[door opens abruptly]

37:06.858 --> 37:08.860
- LIV,
YOU NEED TO SEE THIS.

37:11.963 --> 37:13.699
- WE HEARD
YOU ARRESTED DEDE.

37:13.732 --> 37:15.033
- YOU'RE MAKING A MISTAKE.

37:15.066 --> 37:16.668
- DEDE'S INNOCENT.

37:16.702 --> 37:17.669
- OKAY, WHAT
GIVES YOU THAT IDEA?

37:17.703 --> 37:19.905
- SHE WAS WITH US LAST NIGHT,
THE WHOLE TIME.

37:19.938 --> 37:21.740
AFTER WE LEFT HERE.

37:21.773 --> 37:24.276
- SO MAYBE ONE OF YOU WANTS
TO STEP FORWARD AND CONFESS?

37:24.310 --> 37:26.278
- IT WASN'T ANY OF US.
WE WERE TOGETHER.

37:26.312 --> 37:27.713
ASK THE RESTAURANT...

37:27.746 --> 37:29.715
- THAT'S WHY WE ALL CAME.
TO PROVE IT.

37:29.748 --> 37:31.049
- WELL,
ALL OF YOU AREN'T HERE.

37:31.082 --> 37:33.752
WHERE'S AUDREY?

37:33.785 --> 37:35.321
WAS AUDREY
WITH YOU LAST NIGHT?

37:35.354 --> 37:36.822
- LADIES, YOU DID
THE RIGHT THING BY COMING HERE.

37:36.855 --> 37:38.324
BUT IF YOU DON'T TELL US
EVERYTHING YOU KNOW,

37:38.357 --> 37:41.360
YOU'RE ACCESSORIES
AFTER THE FACT.

37:42.628 --> 37:45.831
- AUDREY WAS WITH US
AT THE BEGINNING.

37:45.864 --> 37:48.534
BUT THEN HER PHONE RANG
AND SHE WENT OUTSIDE TO TAKE IT.

37:48.567 --> 37:49.901
- OKAY,
WHAT TIME WAS THAT?

37:49.935 --> 37:52.938
- 8:30.
SHE NEVER CAME BACK.

37:54.373 --> 37:56.975
[pounding]
- AUDREY, OPEN UP!

37:57.008 --> 38:00.011
- [from inside]
DOOR'S OPEN, OLIVIA.

38:10.922 --> 38:13.792
RELAX.
IF I WERE GOING TO USE IT,

38:13.825 --> 38:16.728
I'D HAVE PLUNGED IT
IN HERE ALREADY.

38:18.764 --> 38:19.731
- YOU KNEW WE WERE COMING.

38:19.765 --> 38:22.934
- OF COURSE.
YOU'RE GOOD COPS.

38:28.807 --> 38:30.542
- WE KNOW ABOUT BUFFALO.

38:30.576 --> 38:33.845
- I'M IMPRESSED.

38:33.879 --> 38:35.781
- YOU ASSAULTED THAT GUY
WITH A BASEBALL BAT.

38:35.814 --> 38:37.416
YOU PUT HIM IN THE HOSPITAL.

38:37.449 --> 38:38.817
WHY?

38:38.850 --> 38:42.488
- HE WAS RAPING 10-YEAR-OLDS.

38:42.521 --> 38:45.391
NEWSPAPER CALLED ME
A LOCAL HERO.

38:45.424 --> 38:46.992
D.A. DECLINED TO PROSECUTE.

38:47.025 --> 38:49.895
AND KEN TURNER
HADN'T BROKEN ANY LAWS.

38:49.928 --> 38:51.763
- DON'T GIVE ME THAT,
STABLER.

38:51.797 --> 38:53.499
YOU WANTED HIM PUNISHED TOO.

38:53.532 --> 38:56.902
- I DID WANT HIM PUNISHED,
NOT DEAD.

38:56.935 --> 38:59.371
- THINK OF THE SUFFERING
I'VE PREVENTED.

38:59.405 --> 39:01.006
ALL THE UNWANTED PREGNANCIES.

39:01.039 --> 39:03.008
[chuckles]
MY OWN,

39:03.041 --> 39:05.844
IF HE'D GOTTEN HIS WAY.

39:05.877 --> 39:08.146
- SO HE CALLED YOU
LAST NIGHT

39:08.179 --> 39:09.815
AFTER SEEING YOU
IN THE PRECINCT.

39:09.848 --> 39:12.618
- WASN'T TWO HOURS
AFTER WE LEFT.

39:12.651 --> 39:15.887
THE GALL OF THAT GUY,
ASKING ME OUT,

39:15.921 --> 39:18.023
INVITING ME
OVER TO DEDE'S PLACE.

39:18.056 --> 39:19.991
- AUDREY, YOU DIDN'T
HAVE TO SAY YES.

39:20.025 --> 39:21.793
- I WAS ABOUT
TO TELL HIM TO GO TO HELL,

39:21.827 --> 39:25.931
BUT...SOMETHING CLICKED.

39:25.964 --> 39:29.401
LIKE WITH
THAT PERV IN BUFFALO.

39:29.435 --> 39:31.102
- SO YOU KNEW
YOU HAD TO GET HIM.

39:31.136 --> 39:33.672
- SOON AS I GET THERE,

39:33.705 --> 39:36.141
HE INVITES ME OUT
INTO THE GARDEN,

39:36.174 --> 39:38.744
STARTS SEDUCING ME.

39:38.777 --> 39:41.580
I TOLD HIM I NEEDED
TO USE THE BATHROOM,

39:41.613 --> 39:43.749
AND I WENT
LOOKING FOR A KNIFE.

39:43.782 --> 39:45.884
FOUND ME A DOOZIE.

39:48.019 --> 39:50.522
I JOINED HIM
IN THE GARDEN...

39:50.556 --> 39:54.760
I JUST MEANT
TO CUT HIS PENIS OFF,

39:54.793 --> 39:58.063
BOOM!
KEN BURSTS OPEN.

39:58.096 --> 40:01.099
[laughing]

40:03.735 --> 40:06.738
- COME ON, AUDREY,
IT'S TIME TO GO.

40:08.139 --> 40:12.911
- PLEASE, OLIVIA.
JUST A FEW MORE SIPS.

40:12.944 --> 40:14.913
THEY DON'T SERVE WINE
WHERE I'M GOING.

